  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Zero brand money.</strong> No supplement company, brand, or manufacturer pays us,
    sponsors us, advertises with us, or sees a grade before you do. None has any influence over
    what we cover or how we grade it.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>No commerce.</strong> We don’t sell supplements, and we never will. There is no shop.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>We grade brands but earn nothing from them.</strong> Where we assess a specific
    product’s quality or labelling, we do it as an independent check, and the fact that we make
    no money from any outcome is exactly what lets you trust it.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>How Somnary is actually funded.</strong> Right now the site is entirely self-funded by
